---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<Layout title="Why Annadel – Annadel Builders Inc." description="Discover what makes Annadel Builders unique - commitment to environmentally conscious methods and beautiful home design.">
  <PageHeader title="Why Annadel" bgImage="/images/Sonoma-Dwelling-by-Annadel-Builders-scaled-1.jpg" />

  <section class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-primary text-[36px]">Sustainable Estate Building in Sonoma &amp; Napa County</h2>
    <div class="w-[71%] mx-auto border-t-[3px] border-muted my-[15px]"></div>
    <p class="mt-6 md:px-[100px]">Partnering with our clients to make their visions come to life is a privilege. Napa, Marin, and Sonoma counties lead the world in lending themselves to outstandingly beautiful home design and construction, and at Annadel Builders, Inc., we are committed to using environmentally conscious methods.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-primary">What Sets our Sonoma County Fine Home Builders Apart</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">Our team at Annadel Builders is dedicated to a culture of excellence, integrity, sustainability, logic, and stewardship in fine home building. We are committed to the following core values:</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-4 list-disc pl-5">
          <li><strong>Smart technology</strong> – Using the most advanced methods and tools available today, Annadel combines timeless standards of service and care with leading-edge technology for the best results for our clients.</li>
          <li><strong>Environmentally conscientious</strong> – Our focus on sustainable home building honors the environments in which we live and work.</li>
          <li><strong>Quality craftsmanship</strong> – At Annadel Builders, our passion is constructing finely built homes for clients with exacting tastes. Our craftsmen and project managers offer a wealth of experience and expertise. From material research and allocation through construction and building occupancy, we provide meticulous attention and oversight through each phase of the project life-cycle for unparalleled results.</li>
          <li><strong>Stewardship &amp; service</strong> – We believe it to be our call of duty to steward our clients' resources well. As diligent and dedicated professionals, you can rely on our team. We establish lasting relationships with our clients that remain long after projects have been completed.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2 space-y-6">
        <img src="/images/Sobre_Vista_32-Kitchen-and-Dining-1-768x570-1.jpg" alt="Luxury kitchen by Annadel Builders" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/Santa-Rosa-Foothills-Fire-Rebuild-sonoma-3-1-1200x800-1.png" alt="Custom home interior" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-8">
    <div class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-[150px] text-center">
      <p><strong>Learn more about our fine home builders and the vision that distinguishes us: <a href="/contact/" class="text-teal hover:underline">Contact Annadel Builders, Inc.</a> today at <a href="tel:7075796282" class="text-teal hover:underline">(707) 579-6282</a> or <a href="mailto:info@annadelbuildersinc.com" class="text-teal hover:underline">info@annadelbuildersinc.com</a> to generate an estimate or to arrange a meeting.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="h-16"></div>
</Layout>
